// Columns
// Responsive multi-column grid layout with configurable gap, alignment, and column count.

FUNCTION getGapClasses(gap) -> string
  Maps gap size prop (sm/md/lg) to Tailwind gap classes.

---

FUNCTION getAlignmentClasses(align) -> string
  Maps alignment prop (start/center/end/stretch) to Tailwind items-* classes.

---

FUNCTION getColumnClasses(columns) -> string
  Maps column count (1–4) to Tailwind grid-cols-* classes with responsive breakpoints.

---

FUNCTION Columns(props) -> ReactNode                                      EXPORT
  Renders a CSS grid container with the configured number of columns, gap, and alignment.
  Children are placed into the grid cells automatically.
